  saturated fat: 17 g
  carbohydrates: 93 g
  sugar: 20 g
  protein: 45 g
  fiber: 7 g
  sodium: 560 mg
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/golden-barbecue-chicken-thighs-5a53a99b2c3e08170161bcc6
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
